Convertir un raster a SpatialPointsDataFrame

## Convertir a SpatialPointsDataFrame de un raster.
library(sp)
library(raster)
med_sp <- as(demMed,"SpatialPointsDataFrame")

Obtener una muestra aletaoria de un SpatialPointsDataFrame

Anlisis exploratorio con bordes.

plot(gmuestraDemMed, borders = bordes)

Estimacin del semivariograma emprico.

semivaralt <- variog(gmuestraDemMed, 
                     uvec = 20,
                     max.dist = 20000)
## variog: computing omnidirectional variogram
plot(semivaralt, las = 1, type = "b", col = "darkblue", pch = 19)

Estimacin de modelo.

mod1 <- likfit(gmuestraDemMed, 
               ini.cov.pars = c(250000, 5000/sqrt(3)),
               cov.model = "gaussian")
## kappa not used for the gaussian correlation function
## ---------------------------------------------------------------
## likfit: likelihood maximisation using the function optim.

plot(semivaralt, las = 1, type = "b", pch = 19, col = "darkgreen")

Prediccin del rea utilizando el borde.

puntos_pred <- pred_grid(c(818000, 845000), c(1174000, 1197000), by = 100)

KC <- krige.control(type = "ok", obj.mod = mod1)
ok <- krige.conv(gmuestraDemMed, krige = KC, loc = puntos_pred,
                 borders = bordes)
## krige.conv: results will be returned only for prediction locations inside the borders
## krige.conv: model with constant mean
## krige.conv: Kriging performed using global neighbourhood

Graficacin del resultado.

pred.lim <- range(c(ok$pred))
sd.lim <- range(sqrt(c(ok$kr)))

image(ok, col = gray(seq(1, 0, l = 51)), zlim = pred.lim,
      las  = 1)
contour(ok, add = T, nlev = 6)
points(gmuestraDemMed, add = TRUE, cex.max = 2)

library(sp)
predAltPDF <- SpatialPixelsDataFrame(locations.inside(puntos_pred, 
                                                   borders = bordes),
                                  data = as.data.frame(ok[1:2]))
proj4string(predAltPDF) <- proj4string(muestraDemMed)
predAltGDF <- as(predAltPDF, "SpatialGridDataFrame")
proj4string(predAltGDF) <- proj4string(muestraDemMed)
plot(predAltPDF)

plot(predAltGDF)

library(tmap)
tm_shape(predAltGDF) +
  tm_raster() +
  tm_layout(legend.outside = TRUE)

library(grid)
mapa1 <- tm_shape(demMed) +

          tm_raster(n = 20)  +
